<!-- Purpose: To test the BDO Element. The BDO Element specifies the base direction of the element's text content. The BDO element requires the DIR attribute to specify the direction of text.  -->

<!-- Expected result: The two sentence used BDO to indicate the direction of the flowing text. The first sentence uses LTR ; The second sentence uses RTL.  -->

<title>XHTML Functional -- BDO</title>

</head>

<body>

The BDO Element specifies the base direction of the element's text

content. <br />

 



<p><bdo dir="LTR">This text flows from left to right as specified

with the DIR attribute in the BDO element.</bdo></p>



<p><bdo dir="RTL">This text flows from right to left as specified

with the DIR attribute in the BDO element.</bdo></p>

</body>

